  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Where can you keep updated on the latest technology news?",
  "response": "Keeping updated on the latest technology news can be accomplished through various sources. Here are some of the most reliable and comprehensive options:\n\n1. **Tech News Websites**:\n   - **TechCrunch**: Focuses on startup stories, product reviews, and major technology trends.\n   - **CNET**: Offers news, product reviews, and comprehensive buying guides.\n   - **The Verge**: Covers everything from devices and software to culture and science.\n   - **Wired**: Provides in-depth tech articles and analysis of industry trends.\n   - **Engadget**: Provides news, reviews, and insightful articles about emerging tech and gadgets.\n\n2. **Technology Sections in Major News Outlets**:\n   - **BBC Technology**: Regular updates on significant global tech news.\n   - **CNN Tech**: Covers the intersection of technology and business.\n   - **The Guardian Tech**: Offers news, features, and insights into the technology industry.\n   - **New York Times Technology**: Articles on the latest advancements and their societal impacts.\n\n3. **Tech Blogs and Forums**:\n   - **Medium \u2013 Technology**: Hosts articles from various writers on tech insights and innovations.\n   - **Hacker News**: A social news website focusing on computer science and entrepreneurship.\n   - **Techdirt**: Offers news on digital disruption and tech-related legal issues.\n\n4. **Social Media and Aggregators**:\n   - **Twitter**: Follow accounts of tech journalists, companies, and influencers.\n   - **Reddit** (r/technology, r/gadgets): Communities discussing the latest in tech news and trends.\n   - **LinkedIn**: Join tech-related groups and follow industry leaders.\n\n5. **Podcasts and YouTube Channels**:\n   - **TWiT (This Week in Tech)**: A network of tech-focused podcasts.\n   - **MKBHD (Marques Brownlee)**: Popular YouTube channel reviewing latest gadgets.\n   - **TechLinked**: Offers concise video news summaries.\n\n6. **News Apps**:\n   - **Feedly**: Customize and gather news from various tech sites.\n   - **Flipboard**: Curates news and articles based on interests.\n\nUsing a combination of these resources will help you stay informed about the latest developments in technology.",
